{
  "stem": "1537.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just sit, the same thing like in Mauthausen, in the tent camp there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the floor, in the mud, there is no place even, to lay down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If-- you are lucky if you find enough place between the-- you know, between the halfling and between the-- the prisoners to sit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Forget it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't go anymore out, anymore, even to get a little soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was already finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only time when they went out for food, I laid down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was waiting to die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- Somehow I didn't care, I didn't know, even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, some boys are telling me, saying, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Herschel, ?] Rubin, the Red Cross is giving out some kind of a little nosh of rye.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what kind of little cake, something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So how shall I get there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is an SS officer, a wild animal, yelling and hitting everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I'm afraid to go there to ask, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because if you are under, I don't know, 17 or something, you were considered a youngster.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was supposed to get a little something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was about, I don't know, 100 feet away from where I was staying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I go there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, Herr officers-- I tell him in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He should-- you know, I'm 16 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he should give me, you know, the portion, what, from the-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had the pistol in the hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] He had this-- a leaded thing like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he gives me a hit over the head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I split my head open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I fell into the mud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And now I'm trying to run away from his eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
